en universe.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.959206717656757e-30, \"text\": \"Aliens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Extraterrestrial_life\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a critically-acclaimed strategy game\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"the Alien universe\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Aliens: Dark Descent, command a squad of hardened Colonial Marines to stop a terrifying Xenomorph outbreak on Planet Lethe,\\\" reads the official description.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\", \"score\": 0.9999999994636255, \"rank\": 5.364087534614072e-10, \"text\": \"Colonial Marines\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Corps_of_Colonial_Marines\"}, {\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"score\": 0.9989083170888351, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xenomorph\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alien_(creature_in_Alien_franchise)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aliens\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"Dark Descent\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"a squad\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"Planet Lethe\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"the official description\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lead your soldiers in real-time combat against iconic Xenomorphs, rogue operatives from the insatiable Weyland-Yutan